<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Lets just say the vast majority of Shadow Knights past lvl 30 truely believe that HT is greatly underpowered.  Even if HT only did 100 dmg at lvl 40 some people would think that was just fine with them.  I'm not calling anyone stupid... however if you like the fact that the ONLY class defining SKILL that we get is Harm Touch and its weak.  Well my fellow Shadow Knights... I really feel sorry for ya if you think that doing only 10 to 15% total damage to a BLUE con mob is just fine  (Once a game day).  To be quite honest I believe it would be more enjoyable to be able to at least do 50% of the total dmg to a High Blue MOB.  Would that make or break the class....Nope...in fact if they took HT away we really wouldnt miss it that much, since we only use it once per day.<p>

Another gripe with HT is the change in % dmg done to the MOB changes (Lowers) in the higher lvls past lvl 30.  Which basically makes it much less useful. <p>

I want to say that I do love playing my Dark Elf Shadow Knight and the spells and HT resistance makes the class more challenging to play.  <p>

Yet we do lack a decent class defining skill in our weak Harm Touch.  Especially considering that most caster classes around lvl 45 can easily out blast our once a day SKILL in one quick dd spell.  40th lvl Necro's for example get a 2000 HP DoT.....compare that to a 40 SK once a day DD skill of 401 dmg....and it is a very weak class skill indead.<p>

Finally the class comparison.  Paladin and the Anti-Paladin (Shadow Knight) 25/lvl LOH and 10/lvl HT  (with some slight increase at higher lvls).  In my opinion this was completely arbitrary and should be improved on the HT side to be at least 20dmg/lvl.<br>
801dmg at lvl 40<br>
Will you solo a yellow con MOB ?  <br>
Hell no<br>
Will this improvement make you all powerful?<br>
Not against 2000 to 8000 HP MOBS<br>
What about PvP?  <br>
Nerf it to half dmg in PvP....Thats not why we want it improved in the first place.. We dont need it for PvP we need it to fight MOBS<p>

Sorry for the long rant....but I said my peace<p>

Kaitan (Circle of Silence)<br>
44 Shadow Knight<br>
Karana Server</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
