<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I think the scope of the SK has been a little lost with this thread. HT is a tool. What other class can deal hundred of point of damage, 0 cast time, while swinging their weapon? We have many tools at our disposal. If SK was nothing but a weakened warrior with HT, I would agree that it would be weak. In the lower levels, it's power is incredible. As you get up in levels, it changes its role. <p>

You find a named mob, dot, dot, pet, hack, fear, dot, hack, ht, dot, dot, etc. This is extremely powerful! I think people want their ht to just be the death touch where I can pull a SG (I am 37-38) and hack it a little and kill it with ht when it has 1/2 life left. THAT is too powerful. If anything, I would like to see HT recharge faster, but I am not complaining.<p>

HT is not an entire class defining ability. Dont treat it as such. Discussing LoH vs HT is apple to oranges. We are NOT anti-paladins. We are shadow knights...</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
