<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Umn guys. This is a message board, so dont get all serious. Now why harm touch is fine. Well his 8 reasons were great. He said to add more if you feel you should well here:<p>

9: Saves your ass. <p>

<br>
Thats what its for. Cloen RIGHT on bro. You guys see  HT isnt for hunting, it aint for KSing (but its fun and funny as hell when u use it for KSing);P Well its suposed to be there to help u out in times when your in trouble. And if your soloing something that it will have no effect on your a dumbass. Your suposed to be in a group. At lvl 52 my shadknight  would rarely solo. It just comes to the point where you cant solo at around lvl 35-40 you cant solo every mob thats gonna give u exp.(u might just need one more person but you still cant solo) Harmtouch is in a group when you need it is a last hit or your groups gonna die, or your healer or nuker did too much damage and has this big ass mob kicking the shit out of him, at that point u use HT as a taunt. So Dont Rag that. HT is Fine. And it doesnt need anything. A few more Damage points per level would kick ass. but were fine. Ah the beauty of SK's soloing was great but were for groups eventualy. Time to end my rambling that I'm typing as I think it. In conclusion DONT COMPLAIN, SK's HAVE IT KICK ASS as it is, oh yeh we could kick the shit out of any enchanter or magician in my opinion.<hr>Xuzk.<br>
